{"tid":975780,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"鑽撚完未呀屌你老母 嬲到我打牆還拖 隻手好撚痛","createTime":"2019-01-10T02:38:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-10T03:23:54.000Z","uid":206344,"like":15,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7e2206189276da98a84784a744ffd32c3a432e7e","tid":975780,"uid":206344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T02:38:24.000Z","msg":"樓上條大陸閪隔一個月裝修一次<br />\n都唔知你成日鑽<br />\n鑽乜鳩<br />\n鑽都算 加埋揼<br />\n兩樣加埋嘈撚到仆街<br />\n仲要鋸 鋸乜柒呀<br />\n你老母臭鳩<br />\n你正職裝修？<br />\n要定期練習？<br />\n隔幾分鐘轉十幾下<br />\n一瞓著又嘈醒<br />\n屌你老母<br />\n啲時機仲準過draymond green啲三分<br />\n嬲撚到我打牆還拖<br />\n而家隻手仲有啲痛添呀<br />\n我就嚟綁起你老母<br />\n綁埋你全家<br />\n現場直播 鑽爆你老母塊閪<br />\n鑽到皮開肉裂<br />\n死大陸閪死全家"},{"pid":"6003dea4ff33ae91bc339d997f275632426986b5","tid":975780,"uid":206344,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T02:40:47.000Z","msg":"好撚嬲呀屌你老母閪 負乜鳩評<br />\n大陸閪有上連登？"},{"pid":"340f18ee65a7ca43ec50cc8e2b0f1abadb54cd88","tid":975780,"uid":197563,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T02:40:58.000Z","msg":"震樓神器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2539628312626c701f30ccb133be1bdefc41693c","tid":975780,"uid":107086,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T02:41:07.000Z","msg":"合情合理，定係你想佢每次鑽之前通知下你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80b89c0cee6b4d884451aea552beff290cc2fed7","tid":975780,"uid":206344,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"340f18ee65a7ca43ec50cc8e2b0f1abadb54cd88","tid":975780,"uid":197563,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T02:40:58.000Z","msg":"震樓神器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T02:41:35.000Z","msg":"啲人話自己都會扣30hp喎"},{"pid":"fa9d6b8f64ce4e73508ec89a70b9e2c62b1a446f","tid":975780,"uid":197563,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"2539628312626c701f30ccb133be1bdefc41693c","tid":975780,"uid":107086,"li